<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>이모저모티콘</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootswatch@4.5.2/dist/minty/bootstrap.min.css" integrity="sha384-H4X+4tKc7b8s4GoMrylmy2ssQYpDHoqzPa9aKXbDwPoPUA3Ra8PA5dGzijN+ePnH" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.0-beta1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.0.js"
        integrity="sha256-H+K7U5CnXl1h5ywQfKtSj8PCmoN9aaq30gDh27Xc0jk=" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.12.4/jquery.min.js"></script>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container" style = "text-align: center;">
        <h1>이모티콘 모두, 저작권 모두, 이모저모티콘</h1>
        <h3>choose your action.</h3>

        <button id="btn_create" class="btn btn-primary">이모티콘 생성하기</button>
        <button id="btn_read" class="btn btn-secondary">이모티콘 정보조회하기</button>
        <button id="btn_transfer" class="btn btn-info">이모티콘 기여하기</button>
        <button id="btn_like" class="btn btn-success">이모티콘 좋아요 누르기</button>
        <p id="network_link"></p>

    </div>
</body>
<script>
    $(function () {
        $('#btn_create').click(function () {
            location.href = '/../public/emo_create.html';
        });
    });
    $(function () {
        $('#btn_read').click(function () {
            location.href = '/../public/emo_read_getHistory.html';
        });
    });
    $(function () {
        $('#btn_transfer').click(function () {
            location.href = '/../public/emo_transfer.html';
        });
    });
    $(function () {
        $('#btn_like').click(function () {
            location.href = '/../public/emo_like.html';
        });
    });
    if (navigator.onLine == true){ 
        document.getElementById("network_link").innerHTML="네트워크 연결 상태 : 정상";
    }else{
        document.getElementById("network_link").innerHTML="네트워크 연결 상태 : 끊어짐";
    }
</script>

</html>
